#: ../../index.rst:7
msgid "CodeVideoRenderer"
msgstr "CodeVideoRenderer"

#: ../../index.rst:9
msgid ""
"**CodeVideoRenderer** is a Python animation library based on Manim, "
"specifically designed for creating dynamic code demonstration videos. It "
"transforms static code into lively animations that simulate real "
"programming processes."
msgstr ""
"**CodeVideoRenderer** 是一个基于 Manim 的 Python 动画库，"
"专为创建动态代码演示视频而设计。它将静态代码转化为生动的动画，"
"模拟真实的编程过程。"

#: ../../index.rst:12
msgid "Core Concepts"
msgstr "核心概念"

#: ../../index.rst:15
msgid "Code Animation"
msgstr "代码动画"

#: ../../index.rst:17
msgid ""
"CodeVideoRenderer's core functionality is to animate code character by "
"character and line by line. Unlike traditional static code displays, it "
"can:"
msgstr ""
"CodeVideoRenderer 的核心功能是逐字符、逐行地为代码添加动画。"
"与传统的静态代码展示不同，它能够："

#: ../../index.rst:19
msgid ""
"**Simulate typing process**: Display code character by character, "
"simulating real programming experience"
msgstr ""
"**模拟打字过程**：逐字符显示代码，模拟真实的编程体验"

#: ../../index.rst:20
msgid ""
"**Intelligent cursor tracking**: Camera automatically follows the cursor "
"movement, ensuring the currently edited code stays in the center of view"
msgstr ""
"**智能光标跟踪**：镜头自动跟随光标移动，确保当前编辑的代码始终位于视野中央"

#: ../../index.rst:21
msgid ""
"**Syntax highlighting support**: Integrates Pygments syntax highlighting "
"engine, supporting multiple programming languages"
msgstr ""
"**语法高亮支持**：集成 Pygments 语法高亮引擎，支持多种编程语言"

#: ../../index.rst:24
msgid "Camera System"
msgstr "镜头系统"

#: ../../index.rst:26
msgid "The library includes an intelligent camera system that can:"
msgstr "该库包含一个智能镜头系统，能够："

#: ../../index.rst:28
msgid "**Auto-scaling**: Automatically adjust camera zoom based on code content"
msgstr "**自动缩放**：根据代码内容自动调整镜头缩放"

#: ../../index.rst:29
msgid ""
"**Smooth movement**: Camera smoothly follows cursor movement, avoiding "
"abrupt jumps"
msgstr "**平滑移动**：镜头平滑跟随光标移动，避免突兀的跳跃"

#: ../../index.rst:30
msgid ""
"**Focus management**: Intelligently recognizes code structure to ensure "
"important parts remain visible"
msgstr "**焦点管理**：智能识别代码结构，确保重要部分始终可见"

#: ../../index.rst:33
msgid "Key Features"
msgstr "主要特性"

#: ../../index.rst:35
msgid ""
"**🎬 Professional animation effects**: Based on Manim engine, providing "
"high-quality animation rendering"
msgstr ""
"**🎬 专业动画效果**：基于 Manim 引擎，提供高质量的动画渲染"

#: ../../index.rst:36
msgid ""
"**📝 Multi-language support**: Syntax highlighting for various programming"
" languages including Python, JavaScript, Java, and more"
msgstr ""
"**📝 多语言支持**：支持多种编程语言的语法高亮，包括 Python、JavaScript、Java 等"

#: ../../index.rst:37
msgid ""
"**⚙️ Highly customizable**: Adjustable typing speed, line spacing, camera"
" behavior, and other parameters"
msgstr ""
"**⚙️ 高度可定制**：可调节打字速度、行间距、镜头行为等参数"

#: ../../index.rst:38
msgid ""
"**🎨 Rich styling**: Multiple code highlighting styles (such as github-"
"dark, monokai, etc.)"
msgstr ""
"**🎨 丰富的样式**：多种代码高亮样式（如 github-dark、monokai 等）"

#: ../../index.rst:39
msgid "**🔧 Dual renderers**: Support for both Cairo and OpenGL rendering backends"
msgstr "**🔧 双渲染器**：支持 Cairo 和 OpenGL 两种渲染后端"

#: ../../index.rst:42
msgid "Use Cases"
msgstr "使用场景"

#: ../../index.rst:44
msgid ""
"CodeVideoRenderer is particularly suitable for the following application "
"scenarios:"
msgstr "CodeVideoRenderer 特别适用于以下应用场景："

#: ../../index.rst:46
msgid ""
"**Educational demonstrations**: Create code explanation videos for "
"programming courses"
msgstr "**教学演示**：为编程课程创建代码讲解视频"

#: ../../index.rst:47
msgid ""
"**Technical presentations**: Make code demonstration segments for "
"conference talks"
msgstr "**技术演讲**：为会议演讲制作代码演示片段"

#: ../../index.rst:48
msgid ""
"**Algorithm visualization**: Dynamically showcase algorithm "
"implementation processes and logic"
msgstr "**算法可视化**：动态展示算法的实现过程和逻辑"

#: ../../index.rst:49
msgid "**Code review**: Visualize code modifications and refactoring processes"
msgstr "**代码审查**：将代码修改和重构过程可视化"

#: ../../index.rst:52
msgid "Design Philosophy"
msgstr "设计理念"

#: ../../index.rst:54
msgid ""
"CodeVideoRenderer's design philosophy is \"making code come alive,\" "
"aiming to better convey programming ideas and code logic through "
"animation. It's not just a code rendering tool, but a code storytelling "
"tool."
msgstr ""
"CodeVideoRenderer 的设计理念是\"让代码活起来\"，"
"旨在通过动画更好地传达编程思想和代码逻辑。"
"它不仅仅是一个代码渲染工具，更是一个代码叙事工具。"

#: ../../index.rst:57
msgid "Index"
msgstr "索引"
